  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Demonstrate the ability of the current interactive tutorial and 1-800 support to teach an AMD
      patient to use the HMP device.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The pilot study purpose is to demonstrate that the tutorial which is part of the device
      software, is giving sufficient training for the intended users.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
